result_data.course_description: Introduction to economic analysis and its application. Theory of supply and demand, costs and revenues of the firm under perfect competition, monopoly and oligopoly, pricing of factors of production, income distribution, and theory of international trade. Econ 1 deals primarily with microeconomics.
important_notes: Course is available to Freshmen and Upperclassmen.
Registration also required for Recitation (see below)
